    <title>LeetCode239 滑动窗口最大值</title>
    <link href="/2025/12/29/leetcode239/"/>
    <url>/2025/12/29/leetcode239/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="题干："><a href="#题干：" class="headerlink" title="题干："></a>题干：</h3><p>参见<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/sliding-window-maximum/description/">题目链接</a></p><p>给你一个整数数组 <code>nums</code>，有一个大小为 <code>k</code> 的滑动窗口从数组的最左侧移动到数组的最右侧。你只可以看到在滑动窗口内的 <code>k</code> 个数字。滑动窗口每次只向右移动一位。</p><p>返回 <em>滑动窗口中的最大值</em> 。</p><p><strong>示例 1：</strong></p><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs subunit">输入：nums = [1,3,<span class="hljs-string">-1</span>,<span class="hljs-string">-3</span>,5,3,6,7], k = 3<br>输出：[3,3,5,5,6,7]<br>解释：<br>滑动窗口的位置                最大值<br>---------------               -----<br>[1  3  <span class="hljs-string">-1</span>] <span class="hljs-string">-3</span>  5  3  6  7       3<br> 1 [3  <span class="hljs-string">-1</span>  <span class="hljs-string">-3</span>] 5  3  6  7       3<br> 1  3 [<span class="hljs-string">-1</span>  <span class="hljs-string">-3</span>  5] 3  6  7       5<br> 1  3  <span class="hljs-string">-1</span> [<span class="hljs-string">-3</span>  5  3] 6  7       5<br> 1  3  <span class="hljs-string">-1</span>  <span class="hljs-string">-3</span> [5  3  6] 7       6<br> 1  3  <span class="hljs-string">-1</span>  <span class="hljs-string">-3</span>  5 [3  6  7]      7<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>示例 2：</strong></p><figure class="highlight inform7"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs inform7">输入：nums = <span class="hljs-comment">[1]</span>, k = 1<br>输出：<span class="hljs-comment">[1]</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-优先队列解法"><a href="#1-优先队列解法" class="headerlink" title="1. 优先队列解法"></a><strong>1. 优先队列解法</strong></h3><p>求窗口中的最大值，很容易想到维护一个优先队列，大顶堆优先队列的头部是最大值。</p><p>优先队列中要存一个 <code>int[2]</code> 的结构，其中，第一个元素是值，第二个元素是下标（用来判断是否在窗口中）。</p><p>对于本题而言，初始时，将数组 nums 的前 k 个元素放入优先队列中。向右移动窗口时，把一个新的元素放入优先队列中，此时堆顶的元素就是堆中所有元素的最大值。</p><p><strong>注意点：</strong></p><p>最大值可能并不在滑动窗口中，因此，再每次取队列头部之前，必须要从大到小剔除窗口外的元素。即</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">// 防止最大值不在窗口中</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(pq.peek()[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] &lt;= i - k)&#123;<br>    pq.poll();<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完整的解题代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] maxSlidingWindow(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> k) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 大顶堆</span><br>        PriorityQueue&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[]&gt; pq = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">PriorityQueue</span>&lt;&gt;((a, b) -&gt; &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] != b[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] ? b[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] - a[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] : b[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] - a[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        &#125;);<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 将第一个窗口加入优先队列</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i ++)&#123;<br>            pq.offer(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[]&#123;nums[i], i&#125;);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化结果</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> [] ans = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n - k + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        ans[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = pq.peek()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> k; i &lt; n; i ++)&#123;<br>            pq.offer(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[]&#123;nums[i], i&#125;);<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 防止最大值不在窗口中</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(pq.peek()[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] &lt;= i - k)&#123;<br>                pq.poll();<br>            &#125;<br>            ans[i - k + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = pq.peek()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ans;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中，时间复杂度为O(n*log(n))，空间复杂度为优先队列占用的O(n)空间</p><h3 id="2-更优化的方法，单调队列"><a href="#2-更优化的方法，单调队列" class="headerlink" title="2. 更优化的方法，单调队列"></a>2. 更优化的方法，单调队列</h3><p>怎样进一步优化呢？</p><p>如果窗口只移动右侧，那么每次最大值就是<code>max(nums[i], lastMax)</code>，现在由于窗口左侧也在移动，导致有可能lastMax被左侧移出窗口，不得不重新找窗口中的最大值。</p><p>换句话说，本题目优化的难点在于<code>如何能够每次窗口移动后，以O(1)的时间复杂度高效找出窗口中的最大值</code>，使用<code>单调队列</code>可以做到这一点。</p><h4 id="2-1-单调队列介绍"><a href="#2-1-单调队列介绍" class="headerlink" title="2.1 单调队列介绍"></a>2.1 单调队列介绍</h4><p>单调队列，毫无疑问就是一个单调的队列，假设保持递减的单调队列，在添加 <code>A</code> 进队列的尾部时，为了保持队列的单调性，会 <code>移除</code> 小于 <code>A</code> 的所有元素，例如，待插入顺序为: 1,3,-1,-3,5,3,6,7</p><p>单调队列为：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">队列</th><th align="center">插入值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">头[1]尾</td><td align="center">1</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[3]尾</td><td align="center">3</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[3, - 1]尾</td><td align="center">-1</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[3, -1, -3]尾</td><td align="center">-3</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[5]尾</td><td align="center">5</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[5, 3]尾</td><td align="center">3</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[6]尾</td><td align="center">6</td></tr><tr><td align="center">头[7]尾</td><td align="center">7</td></tr></tbody></table><p>显然，单调队列的队首，就是最大值。</p><p>如果将单调队列应用于本题，只需要保证单调队列中 <code>只 包含窗口内的值</code> 即可。</p><p>如图所示：<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/sliding-window-maximum/solutions/2361228/239-hua-dong-chuang-kou-zui-da-zhi-dan-d-u6h0/">来源</a></p><img src="/img/leetcode239/1.png" style="zoom: 67%;" /><h4 id="2-2-算法流程："><a href="#2-2-算法流程：" class="headerlink" title="2.2 算法流程："></a><strong>2.2 算法流程：</strong></h4><ol><li>初始化： 双端队列 deque ，结果列表 res ，数组长度 n ；</li><li>若 i&gt;0 且 队首元素 deque[0] &#x3D; 被删除元素 nums[i−1] ：则队首元素出队；</li><li>删除 deque 内所有 &lt;nums[j] 的元素，以保持 deque 递减；</li><li>将 nums[j] 添加至 deque 尾部；</li></ol><h4 id="2-3-为什么可以这么做呢？"><a href="#2-3-为什么可以这么做呢？" class="headerlink" title="2.3 为什么可以这么做呢？"></a>2.3 为什么可以这么做呢？</h4><p>假设窗口内存在 i , j ，且nums[i] &lt; nums[j] ，那么在向右移动窗口时，只要 i 还在窗口里，最大值就不可能是 i ，也就是说，i是无效的。</p><p>因此，单调队列将无用的 i 去除了，每次只留下 j ，就能优化优先队列冗余的存储，也加快了计算</p><h4 id="2-4-代码实现"><a href="#2-4-代码实现" class="headerlink" title="2.4 代码实现"></a>2.4 代码实现</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] maxSlidingWindow(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> k) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> || k == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化</span><br>        Deque&lt;Integer&gt; deque = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">LinkedList</span>&lt;&gt;();<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> [] res = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n - k + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化窗口</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 双端队列</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i ++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(!deque.isEmpty() &amp;&amp; deque.peekLast() &lt; nums[i])&#123;<br>                deque.removeLast();<br>            &#125;<br>            deque.addLast(nums[i]);<br>        &#125;<br>        res[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = deque.peekFirst();<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 遍历并维护单调队列</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> k; i &lt; n; i ++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(deque.peekFirst() == nums[i - k])&#123;<br>                deque.removeFirst();<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 维护单调</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(!deque.isEmpty() &amp;&amp; deque.peekLast() &lt; nums[i])&#123;<br>                deque.removeLast();<br>            &#125;<br>            deque.addLast(nums[i]);<br>            res[i - k + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = deque.peekFirst();<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
